The paper discusses the performance analysis of cache networks, which are a key component of content-oriented Internet architectures. This topic is closely related to network infrastructure (cs.NI), distributed systems (cs.DS), social and information networks (cs.SI), information theory (cs.IT), and performance analysis (cs.PF). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
